<promed@promedmail.org>
[Regardless of whether this is an epidemic or merely an ´outbreak´,
the remarkable thing is that the police & health department are
speaking publicly about cholera in the country. Pakistan has not
reported a single case of cholera to WHO in years, although the
disease in endemic there. - Mod.JW
